**LIST METHODS & OPERATIONS**
1) Adding items to the list;
to add at end we use append()
to add at index 1 we use insert()
2) Removing items to the list;
to remove by value we use remove()
to remove the last item we use pop()
to remove all items we use clear()
3) Other Useful Methods --> sort() and reverse()
sort() -- to sort in a particular order
reverse() -- reverses the elements in the list
* numbers = [1,7,5,3]
* numbers.sort() --> [1,3,5,7]
* numbers.reverse() --> [7,5,3,1]
len(numbers) -- 4
max(numbers) -- 7
min(numbers) -- 1
